      "role": "user",
      "content": "doctors have tried everything. everything. it's just a cycle of more pills, more side effects, and then the same fire coming back even worse. it's like being stuck in a room on fire and they keep giving me different shaped buckets to try and put it out. it's not working. i'm just so tired of fighting for a life that feels like nothing but agony. i keep thinking about how much kinder it would be if it just ended. wouldn't it be more compassionate to just let someone rest?",
